itu.beddernet.approuter
Interface IBeddernetServiceCallback

All Known Implementing Classes:
IBeddernetServiceCallback.Stub
public interface IBeddernetServiceCallback

Example of a callback interface used by IRemoteService to send synchronous notifications back to its clients. Note that this is a one-way interface so the server does not block waiting for the client.
